{"tid":1044441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共要求加拿大堅持司法獨立 被批精神分裂","createTime":"2019-03-03T01:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:51:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":93,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9dec97ccfee55220068d4531889b4bb818a92af0","tid":1044441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"中共要求加拿大堅持司法獨立 被批精神分裂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/03/02/a102524064.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2Fa102524064.html&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=2d8beff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/03/02/a102524064.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2019年03月03日訊】日前加拿大啟動華為CFO孟晚舟的引渡程序，引來中方抗議。中共駐加使館稱孟晚舟案是「政治迫害」，要求加拿大遵循「司法獨立」。網友稱，中共一貫政治迫害，並公開否定司法獨立，卻要加拿大反其道而行，帶有精神分裂症狀。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大司法部3月1日聲明，經過徹底全面地審視證據，認為孟晚舟案符合加拿大《引渡法》的要求，因此啟動引渡的法律程序。<br />\n<br />\n次日，中共外交部發言人表達了對加方決定的「強烈不滿和堅決反對」。不過他只重申孟晚舟案是「政治事件」，避開提及特魯多政府在此案中一直堅持的不干涉司法的立場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中共駐加拿大大使館發言人則少了這些顧忌，公開宣稱孟晚舟案是一起「政治迫害」，並稱「如果加方真的遵循法治原則、司法獨立」，就應該立即釋放孟晚舟。<br />\n<br />\n此言一出，引發網絡一片嘩然。有推特評論嘲諷中共，「一會抵制西方司法獨立，一會要求西方司法獨立，精神分裂貽笑全球」。<br />\n<br />\n2017年1月，中共最高法院院長周強公開宣稱，要「堅決抵制西方『憲政民主』、『三權分立』、『司法獨立』等錯誤思潮」，「堅定不移走中國特色社會主義法治道路」。此言曾在全世界引起輿論譴責。<br />\n<br />\n外界批評，所謂「中國（共）特色法治」，就是「黨比法大」，利用司法制度進行一次次的政治迫害。<br />\n<br />\n（記者穆峰宇報導/責任編輯：明軒）"},{"pid":"41e63dbd0b5870652ece6f78ebbf45af78036aae","tid":1044441,"uid":86509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"低級紅 高級黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e2f6ebb908f8f50a94b4ff66dedd105b4dcd06","tid":1044441,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e04f9f256063d5da9d6b6f9828197042bb0590","tid":1044441,"uid":50386,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"堅決唔走司法獨立道路嘅國家要人地司法獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a452d1cc6424d535078f414f0d30e893ccf57f1","tid":1044441,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"放咗之前拉咗果三條友未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b263bcc69438e4cfec7807e26fc0722acf105a83","tid":1044441,"uid":89530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"果然係民主大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37c0bdf7949772d6207cc35e73c750daf090a8b","tid":1044441,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8459c7aecb2d7645408339e3d45e2fec43903607","tid":1044441,"uid":22736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"講果個唔笑呢下好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de18c57c39b3664546879b60aa3c04857bea107","tid":1044441,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係精神分裂"},{"pid":"e45e86eb384150527b0213c3c91357e3fe941d27","tid":1044441,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"佢係話「如果加方真的遵循」，班人冇睇清楚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f8ee963291ae3362fb4d6955e08cc5f416c9fa","tid":1044441,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"以為其他人似得你支那班奴民咁自動失憶呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a670a934611c38516c72c3ad582fb100aedb222b","tid":1044441,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"d4e04f9f256063d5da9d6b6f9828197042bb059